1
00:00:02.225 --> 00:00:07.783 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>SISKO:</c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i> Station Log, Stardate 47182.1.</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>DS9 has been temporarily evacuated</i></c.bg_transparent>

2
00:00:07.783 --> 00:00:11.362 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>due to a violent plasma disruption.</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>Until the disturbance ends,</i></c.bg_transparent>

3
00:00:11.383 --> 00:00:13.924 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>we'll be forced to maintain the station</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>with a skeleton crew.</i></c.bg_transparent>

4
00:00:14.576 --> 00:00:16.936 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-How are we holding up?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-So far, so good.</c.bg_transparent>

5
00:00:16.936 --> 00:00:19.677 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll say one thing for the Cardassians,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>they built this place to last.</c.bg_transparent>

6
00:00:19.615 --> 00:00:20.815 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Just in case it doesn't...</c.bg_transparent>

7
00:00:21.433 --> 00:00:23.814 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've got the </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Orinoco</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>prepped and ready at Pad C.</c.bg_transparent>

8
00:00:24.673 --> 00:00:25.952 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Any word from Chief O'Brien?</c.bg_transparent>

9
00:00:26.033 --> 00:00:28.154 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He and Odo checked in about an hour ago.</c.bg_transparent>

10
00:00:27.591 --> 00:00:29.871 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>They sealed off the airlocks</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in the upper and lower pylons</c.bg_transparent>

11
00:00:29.951 --> 00:00:31.551 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>and were moving on to the docking ring.</c.bg_transparent>

12
00:00:32.270 --> 00:00:34.230 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Sisko to O'Brien.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>-O'Brien here.</i></c.bg_transparent>

13
00:00:34.471 --> 00:00:36.832 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-What's your status, Chief?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Almost done, Commander.</c.bg_transparent>

14
00:00:37.649 --> 00:00:40.568 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We've sealed all the airlocks</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>on levels 21, 22, and 23.</c.bg_transparent>

15
00:00:41.367 --> 00:00:42.688 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We still have to check the outer bulkheads</c.bg_transparent>

16
00:00:43.127 --> 00:00:45.048 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>to make sure there hasn't been</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>any crystallization</c.bg_transparent>

17
00:00:45.048 --> 00:00:47.229 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>from the plasma discharges.</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>It shouldn't take too long.</i></c.bg_transparent>

18
00:00:47.446 --> 00:00:48.327 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>O'Brien out.</c.bg_transparent>

19
00:00:50.486 --> 00:00:51.686 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( faint banging )</c.bg_transparent>

20
00:00:53.046 --> 00:00:54.405 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Did you hear that?</c.bg_transparent>

21
00:00:55.370 --> 00:00:55.964 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hear what?</c.bg_transparent>

22
00:00:56.045 --> 00:00:58.044 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I could have sworn I heard something.</c.bg_transparent>

23
00:01:02.282 --> 00:01:04.002 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Quark!</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-What are you doing here?</c.bg_transparent>

24
00:01:04.281 --> 00:01:06.762 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>ODO: You're under strict orders from Sisko</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to stay in the bar.</c.bg_transparent>

25
00:01:07.520 --> 00:01:10.759 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm not a prisoner, Odo.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I volunteered to stay</c.bg_transparent>

26
00:01:10.839 --> 00:01:12.279 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>and help you protect the station.</c.bg_transparent>

27
00:01:12.279 --> 00:01:15.402 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The only reason you volunteered</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>is because there wasn't enough room</c.bg_transparent>

28
00:01:15.402 --> 00:01:19.279 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>on the evacuation shuttles</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for 600 bars of gold-pressed latinum</c.bg_transparent>

29
00:01:19.576 --> 00:01:21.157 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>which still doesn't explain</c.bg_transparent>

30
00:01:21.157 --> 00:01:23.198 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>what you're doing out here</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in the docking ring.</c.bg_transparent>

31
00:01:25.315 --> 00:01:27.556 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was saying good-bye to my brother.</c.bg_transparent>

32
00:01:27.953 --> 00:01:31.633 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Your brother?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>His shuttle left three hours ago.</c.bg_transparent>

33
00:01:32.472 --> 00:01:36.815 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Funny... it's only been three hours</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and I'm already lost without him.</c.bg_transparent>

34
00:01:37.111 --> 00:01:38.590 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, please!</c.bg_transparent>

35
00:01:38.790 --> 00:01:40.651 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't try to tell me</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you've been sitting out here</c.bg_transparent>

36
00:01:40.651 --> 00:01:42.702 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>all this time pining for Rom.</c.bg_transparent>

37
00:01:44.130 --> 00:01:44.450 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I know, I know.</c.bg_transparent>

38
00:01:45.489 --> 00:01:47.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He couldn't find a cup of water</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>if you dropped him in a lake,</c.bg_transparent>

39
00:01:47.908 --> 00:01:52.331 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but even if he is an idiot,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>he's still my brother.</c.bg_transparent>

40
00:01:52.846 --> 00:01:56.448 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>And you'd betray him in a second</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>if it suited your interests.</c.bg_transparent>

41
00:01:56.985 --> 00:01:58.646 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That doesn't mean I don't love him.</c.bg_transparent>

42
00:01:58.784 --> 00:01:59.585 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( Odo scoffs )</c.bg_transparent>

43
00:02:00.296 --> 00:02:04.619 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Chief, do you have any brothers?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-As a matter of fact, I have two.</c.bg_transparent>

44
00:02:05.650 --> 00:02:07.431 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>And did you ever have</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to say good-bye to them?</c.bg_transparent>

45
00:02:07.782 --> 00:02:11.341 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Sure, when I joined Starfleet.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-And did it bring a tear to your eye?</c.bg_transparent>

46
00:02:13.380 --> 00:02:14.379 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I suppose so.</c.bg_transparent>

47
00:02:14.580 --> 00:02:17.742 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, try explaining that to him.</c.bg_transparent>

48
00:04:24.961 --> 00:04:26.610 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>The storm's intensity is up 37%.</c.bg_transparent>

49
00:04:27.240 --> 00:04:29.039 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is there any way of telling</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>how long it'll last?</c.bg_transparent>

50
00:04:29.540 --> 00:04:32.862 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Your guess is as good as mine.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Plasma storms are extremely rare.</c.bg_transparent>

51
00:04:33.239 --> 00:04:34.600 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>But look on the bright side.</c.bg_transparent>

52
00:04:34.600 --> 00:04:36.630 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>This gives us a great</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>opportunity to study one.</c.bg_transparent>

53
00:04:36.738 --> 00:04:37.639 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, lucky us.</c.bg_transparent>

54
00:04:37.717 --> 00:04:39.398 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>You should see the view</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>from the Promenade.</c.bg_transparent>

55
00:04:39.477 --> 00:04:40.676 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's simply amazing.</c.bg_transparent>

56
00:04:40.756 --> 00:04:44.509 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>-I assume the Promenade is secure.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Oh, yes, sir. I've struck the sails</c.bg_transparent>

57
00:04:44.509 --> 00:04:45.873 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>and battened the hatches, so to speak.</c.bg_transparent>

58
00:04:46.700 --> 00:04:48.468 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>DAX: Benjamin,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you better take a look at this.</c.bg_transparent>

59
00:04:49.587 --> 00:04:51.507 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>( console beeping insistently )</c.bg_transparent>

60
00:04:52.133 --> 00:04:55.195 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm detecting a small vessel</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>headed this way at one quarter impulse.</c.bg_transparent>

61
00:04:56.131 --> 00:04:58.011 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>-KIRA: They're hailing us.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-On screen.</c.bg_transparent>

62
00:05:00.170 --> 00:05:01.410 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>I can't get a visual.</c.bg_transparent>

63
00:05:01.810 --> 00:05:03.849 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>MAN: ( static )</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>This is the Cargo Ship </i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>Ekina.</c.bg_transparent>

64
00:05:04.209 --> 00:05:05.769 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>We've been caught by the storm.</i></c.bg_transparent>

65
00:05:05.929 --> 00:05:08.528 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Our engines have been severely damaged.</i></c.bg_transparent>

66
00:05:08.935 --> 00:05:11.967 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>We need emergency assistance.</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>Can you read me?</i></c.bg_transparent>

67
00:05:12.046 --> 00:05:14.486 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Repeat, this is the Cargo Ship </i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>Ekina</c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>...</i></c.bg_transparent>

68
00:05:16.126 --> 00:05:17.125 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've lost it.</c.bg_transparent>

69
00:05:18.605 --> 00:05:20.146 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Can we get a transporter lock on the crew?</c.bg_transparent>

70
00:05:21.923 --> 00:05:23.723 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No, there's too much interference.</c.bg_transparent>

71
00:05:24.143 --> 00:05:27.345 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Engage the tractor beam.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Bring them in to the closest docking bay.</c.bg_transparent>

72
00:05:27.702 --> 00:05:29.542 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>There might be casualties.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I'll get down to the Infirmary.</c.bg_transparent>

73
00:05:29.741 --> 00:05:30.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>SISKO: Good idea.</c.bg_transparent>

74
00:05:31.724 --> 00:05:33.683 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Sisko to O'Brien.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>-</i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>O'Brien here.</c.bg_transparent>

75
00:05:34.284 --> 00:05:37.482 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Chief, we've got some storm victims</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>coming in to Docking Bay Five</i></c.bg_transparent>

76
00:05:37.482 --> 00:05:38.812 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>who may be in need of assistance.</i></c.bg_transparent>

77
00:05:39.339 --> 00:05:40.820 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll have to release the emergency seal</c.bg_transparent>

78
00:05:40.820 --> 00:05:42.431 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>on the airlock before</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>they can board the station.</c.bg_transparent>

79
00:05:42.431 --> 00:05:43.084 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>On my way.</c.bg_transparent>

80
00:05:55.347 --> 00:05:55.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Stand clear.</c.bg_transparent>

81
00:05:59.986 --> 00:06:01.105 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( coughing )</c.bg_transparent>

82
00:06:02.051 --> 00:06:03.492 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Are you all right? Is anyone hurt?</c.bg_transparent>

83
00:06:04.263 --> 00:06:04.651 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>KLINGON: Not yet.</c.bg_transparent>

84
00:06:05.511 --> 00:06:07.693 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-What the hell do you think you're doing?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-No questions.</c.bg_transparent>

85
00:06:08.250 --> 00:06:11.052 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>This is a nice way to show your gratitude.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>We just saved your lives out there.</c.bg_transparent>

86
00:06:11.189 --> 00:06:14.651 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You see? The ever-helpful Federation.</c.bg_transparent>

87
00:06:15.628 --> 00:06:17.489 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-So predictable.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Listen, friend</c.bg_transparent>

88
00:06:17.489 --> 00:06:18.639 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>in case you haven't heard</c.bg_transparent>

89
00:06:18.967 --> 00:06:21.349 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>the Federation and the Klingon</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Empire are allies now.</c.bg_transparent>

90
00:06:21.366 --> 00:06:22.166 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( spits )</c.bg_transparent>

91
00:06:22.845 --> 00:06:24.166 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Empire is governed</c.bg_transparent>

92
00:06:24.265 --> 00:06:26.907 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>by doddering fools</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and frightened old women</c.bg_transparent>

93
00:06:27.184 --> 00:06:29.486 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>who aren't worthy of the name "Klingon."</c.bg_transparent>

94
00:06:30.704 --> 00:06:32.502 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mareel! The combadge.</c.bg_transparent>

95
00:06:34.642 --> 00:06:38.525 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-This one must be the shape-shifter.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Go on! What are you waiting for?</c.bg_transparent>

96
00:06:46.078 --> 00:06:47.198 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're a Trill.</c.bg_transparent>

97
00:06:51.137 --> 00:06:53.599 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You! Shifter! Inside.</c.bg_transparent>

98
00:06:55.616 --> 00:06:56.917 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And what if I refuse?</c.bg_transparent>

99
00:06:57.975 --> 00:07:01.214 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Please, do as he says</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and no one will get hurt.</c.bg_transparent>

100
00:07:01.973 --> 00:07:05.333 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>KLINGON: Now! Or this one dies.</c.bg_transparent>

101
00:07:27.925 --> 00:07:29.146 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Let's go...</c.bg_transparent>

102
00:07:29.166 --> 00:07:30.525 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ally.</c.bg_transparent>

103
00:07:36.603 --> 00:07:38.004 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Chief, were there any casualties?</c.bg_transparent>

104
00:07:38.123 --> 00:07:40.523 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-That depends on you.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-BASHIR: What's this all about?</c.bg_transparent>

105
00:07:40.602 --> 00:07:41.442 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( grunts )</c.bg_transparent>

106
00:07:41.522 --> 00:07:43.362 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yeto, get the Ferengi.</c.bg_transparent>

107
00:07:44.201 --> 00:07:46.760 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Any more questions?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Don't hurt him.</c.bg_transparent>

108
00:07:47.760 --> 00:07:49.520 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mareel! The box.</c.bg_transparent>

109
00:07:51.359 --> 00:07:56.002 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Put it in your stasis chamber.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Now, or I will destroy it.</c.bg_transparent>

110
00:07:57.198 --> 00:07:58.717 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is that supposed</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to be some kind of threat?</c.bg_transparent>

111
00:07:59.357 --> 00:08:00.637 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They've got Odo in there.</c.bg_transparent>

112
00:08:02.695 --> 00:08:05.757 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I see... Well, in that case...</c.bg_transparent>

113
00:08:19.891 --> 00:08:23.077 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm still not getting a response</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>from O'Brien or Odo.</c.bg_transparent>

114
00:08:22.530 --> 00:08:23.969 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Run a level-3 security scan.</c.bg_transparent>

115
00:08:24.769 --> 00:08:25.809 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>KLINGON: Don't bother.</c.bg_transparent>

116
00:08:28.408 --> 00:08:32.087 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Please, take your hands</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>away from the controls.</c.bg_transparent>

117
00:08:33.726 --> 00:08:34.526 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Now!</c.bg_transparent>

118
00:08:36.326 --> 00:08:37.805 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Get to the center of the room.</c.bg_transparent>

119
00:08:41.564 --> 00:08:42.684 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Do as he says.</c.bg_transparent>

120
00:08:51.100 --> 00:08:52.401 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't worry, Verad.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>It's going to be all right.</c.bg_transparent>

121
00:09:08.996 --> 00:09:11.076 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Get with the others. Move!</c.bg_transparent>

122
00:09:13.754 --> 00:09:15.473 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Your turn, little man.</c.bg_transparent>

123
00:09:21.392 --> 00:09:24.311 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't forget to disable the backups</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>as well as the primary systems.</c.bg_transparent>

124
00:09:28.650 --> 00:09:31.652 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's my fault, Commander.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>They caught us by surprise.</c.bg_transparent>

125
00:09:32.748 --> 00:09:35.510 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Somehow, they must have neutralized</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the security systems</c.bg_transparent>

126
00:09:35.510 --> 00:09:37.480 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-in the docking ring.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-How did they manage that?</c.bg_transparent>

127
00:09:37.909 --> 00:09:40.108 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm not sure but I've got</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a pretty good idea.</c.bg_transparent>

128
00:09:40.469 --> 00:09:42.749 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We ran across Quark</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in an airlock a little while ago.</c.bg_transparent>

129
00:09:44.387 --> 00:09:47.627 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>When this is over Quark</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and I are going to have a little talk.</c.bg_transparent>

130
00:09:56.461 --> 00:09:57.222 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Do you know him?</c.bg_transparent>

131
00:10:12.097 --> 00:10:13.496 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ah, Yeto.</c.bg_transparent>

132
00:10:14.417 --> 00:10:16.976 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's such a pleasure</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>doing business with Klingons.</c.bg_transparent>

133
00:10:17.055 --> 00:10:20.054 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're so, um... punctual.</c.bg_transparent>

134
00:10:20.974 --> 00:10:23.696 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I see your ship was rescued</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>according to plan.</c.bg_transparent>

135
00:10:24.253 --> 00:10:26.795 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Um, I've got your merchandise right here</c.bg_transparent>

136
00:10:27.753 --> 00:10:29.774 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-but I don't see any latinum.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-You Ferengi!</c.bg_transparent>

137
00:10:30.412 --> 00:10:33.634 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You think you're so clever,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but you're stupid.</c.bg_transparent>

138
00:10:33.670 --> 00:10:36.172 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Now, now, there's no need</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for name-calling.</c.bg_transparent>

139
00:10:37.210 --> 00:10:39.352 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you don't want</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>these liquid data chains,</c.bg_transparent>

140
00:10:39.809 --> 00:10:42.168 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm sure I can line up</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>dozens of other buyers.</c.bg_transparent>

141
00:10:42.267 --> 00:10:43.648 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Go right ahead.</c.bg_transparent>

142
00:10:44.588 --> 00:10:45.387 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yeto,</c.bg_transparent>

143
00:10:45.467 --> 00:10:47.989 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>you expect me to believe</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that you've come all this way,</c.bg_transparent>

144
00:10:48.406 --> 00:10:51.948 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>braved the storm, just to tell me</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that the deal is off?</c.bg_transparent>

145
00:10:52.525 --> 00:10:53.724 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Stupid Ferengi!</c.bg_transparent>

146
00:10:54.284 --> 00:10:55.483 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( chuckling nervously )</c.bg_transparent>

147
00:10:57.203 --> 00:11:00.523 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-I said no one moves.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I'm Commander of this station.</c.bg_transparent>

148
00:11:00.523 --> 00:11:03.765 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-What is your business here?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-You'll have to ask my employer.</c.bg_transparent>

149
00:11:09.221 --> 00:11:14.544 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm... I'm sorry about all this.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>If everyone would just cooperate</c.bg_transparent>

150
00:11:14.878 --> 00:11:18.101 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-I promise it will all be over soon.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-What will be over soon?</c.bg_transparent>

151
00:11:18.757 --> 00:11:21.836 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>QUARK: This is an outrage!</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I demand to be released at once!</c.bg_transparent>

152
00:11:21.956 --> 00:11:23.835 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Enough of your whining!</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Who are these people?</c.bg_transparent>

153
00:11:23.915 --> 00:11:24.955 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What do they want from us?</c.bg_transparent>

154
00:11:25.035 --> 00:11:27.554 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Funny. I was about</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to ask you that question.</c.bg_transparent>

155
00:11:27.634 --> 00:11:29.613 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-That's enough.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-SISKO: I agree.</c.bg_transparent>

156
00:11:29.393 --> 00:11:30.594 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Now tell me what you want here.</c.bg_transparent>

157
00:11:34.112 --> 00:11:34.912 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Dax.</c.bg_transparent>

158
00:11:36.632 --> 00:11:38.871 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I... want Dax.</c.bg_transparent>

159
00:11:40.210 --> 00:11:44.013 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-She's not going anywhere with you.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-No, no. I don't want the girl.</c.bg_transparent>

160
00:11:44.029 --> 00:11:49.753 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I only want what is rightfully mine...</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>What should have been mine years ago.</c.bg_transparent>

161
00:11:53.947 --> 00:11:55.546 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I want Dax.</c.bg_transparent>

162
00:11:56.705 --> 00:12:01.184 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>DAX: The symbiont, Benjamin.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>He's come to steal my symbiont.</c.bg_transparent>

163
00:12:11.461 --> 00:12:15.020 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You can't remove Jadzia's symbiont.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>If you do, she'll die.</c.bg_transparent>

164
00:12:16.352 --> 00:12:17.219 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He knows that, Doctor.</c.bg_transparent>

165
00:12:18.745 --> 00:12:18.659 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm...</c.bg_transparent>

166
00:12:19.919 --> 00:12:24.502 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm sorry about all this.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Please, believe me,</c.bg_transparent>

167
00:12:24.839 --> 00:12:28.061 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-I wish I didn't have to do this.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Then don't.</c.bg_transparent>

168
00:12:30.116 --> 00:12:31.277 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't have a choice.</c.bg_transparent>

169
00:12:32.161 --> 00:12:36.904 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I... spent my whole life</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>trying to qualify for the joining.</c.bg_transparent>

170
00:12:37.154 --> 00:12:42.798 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I... studied constantly,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>every day, every waking hour.</c.bg_transparent>

171
00:12:44.252 --> 00:12:47.474 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I sacrificed... everything,</c.bg_transparent>

172
00:12:47.630 --> 00:12:51.453 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and then I went before</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the symbiosis evaluation board</c.bg_transparent>

173
00:12:51.469 --> 00:12:52.269 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And...</c.bg_transparent>

174
00:12:53.588 --> 00:12:57.871 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They reduced my entire life to one word...</c.bg_transparent>

175
00:12:59.547 --> 00:13:01.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Unsuitable.</c.bg_transparent>

176
00:13:02.766 --> 00:13:04.727 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's nothing to be ashamed of.</c.bg_transparent>

177
00:13:05.365 --> 00:13:08.427 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Neither of my parents</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>or my sister underwent symbiosis,</c.bg_transparent>

178
00:13:09.324 --> 00:13:11.386 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and they live happy</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and productive lives.</c.bg_transparent>

179
00:13:11.603 --> 00:13:14.465 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Only one Trill in ten</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>is chosen to be joined.</c.bg_transparent>

180
00:13:15.060 --> 00:13:16.901 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's easy for you to say.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>They chose you.</c.bg_transparent>

181
00:13:17.981 --> 00:13:19.502 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was one of the lucky ones.</c.bg_transparent>

182
00:13:19.901 --> 00:13:21.562 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Now it's Verad's time to be lucky.</c.bg_transparent>

183
00:13:22.220 --> 00:13:23.300 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>KIRA: Why Dax?</c.bg_transparent>

184
00:13:23.900 --> 00:13:26.659 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>There are thousands</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of symbionts on Trill. Why her?</c.bg_transparent>

185
00:13:27.079 --> 00:13:28.680 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I did research. I worked it all out.</c.bg_transparent>

186
00:13:29.098 --> 00:13:31.880 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Dax symbiont is the best match for me.</c.bg_transparent>

187
00:13:31.880 --> 00:13:35.021 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We have mutual interests,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>science, diplomacy--</c.bg_transparent>

188
00:13:35.719 --> 00:13:38.298 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Verad, there is another reason,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>isn't there?</c.bg_transparent>

189
00:13:39.337 --> 00:13:40.256 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>SISKO: The wormhole.</c.bg_transparent>

190
00:13:41.554 --> 00:13:43.075 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>After you've stolen the symbiont</c.bg_transparent>

191
00:13:43.075 --> 00:13:45.133 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>you plan on escaping</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to the Gamma Quadrant, don't you?</c.bg_transparent>

192
00:13:45.793 --> 00:13:47.775 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Can you think of a better place</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to start a new life?</c.bg_transparent>

193
00:13:48.172 --> 00:13:51.835 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I understand your frustration</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but there could be dozens of reasons</c.bg_transparent>

194
00:13:51.835 --> 00:13:53.974 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>why the board</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>didn't select you for symbiosis.</c.bg_transparent>

195
00:13:54.350 --> 00:13:56.151 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They have to be very careful.</c.bg_transparent>

196
00:13:56.969 --> 00:14:00.191 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>An improper joining</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>can cause permanent psychological damage</c.bg_transparent>

197
00:14:01.008 --> 00:14:03.368 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>to both the symbiont and the host.</c.bg_transparent>

198
00:14:04.367 --> 00:14:06.327 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>They were only looking</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>after your best interests.</c.bg_transparent>

199
00:14:06.627 --> 00:14:08.629 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Your best interests maybe, but not mine.</c.bg_transparent>

200
00:14:09.466 --> 00:14:14.544 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>All they've done is condemn me</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to a life of... of...</c.bg_transparent>

201
00:14:17.084 --> 00:14:18.005 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mediocrity.</c.bg_transparent>

202
00:14:18.005 --> 00:14:19.855 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, I refuse to accept that.</c.bg_transparent>

203
00:14:19.882 --> 00:14:22.984 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I--I'm not going to spend</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the rest of my life dreaming</c.bg_transparent>

204
00:14:23.721 --> 00:14:27.801 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>about what I could have been.</c.bg_transparent>

205
00:14:28.720 --> 00:14:34.038 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>What I should have been.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I deserve... more...</c.bg_transparent>

206
00:14:34.998 --> 00:14:39.241 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-and I'm going to get it.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Yeto, T'Kar, it's time.</c.bg_transparent>

207
00:14:42.220 --> 00:14:43.716 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll have no part in this.</c.bg_transparent>

208
00:14:45.603 --> 00:14:46.914 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I... I understand.</c.bg_transparent>

209
00:14:47.634 --> 00:14:48.514 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( groans )</c.bg_transparent>

210
00:14:51.913 --> 00:14:52.833 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( gasping )</c.bg_transparent>

211
00:14:53.153 --> 00:14:54.713 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>VERAD: Keep away from him, Doctor.</c.bg_transparent>

212
00:14:58.472 --> 00:15:00.792 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There, you see? I've taken the first step.</c.bg_transparent>

213
00:15:03.649 --> 00:15:05.871 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Even if I don't get what I want,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>my life is over,</c.bg_transparent>

214
00:15:05.997 --> 00:15:10.400 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>so either you help me</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>or you and your friends will die.</c.bg_transparent>

215
00:15:10.407 --> 00:15:11.548 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's your choice.</c.bg_transparent>

216
00:15:13.057 --> 00:15:13.968 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He'll help.</c.bg_transparent>

217
00:15:15.446 --> 00:15:17.348 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't want anyone else hurt</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>because of me.</c.bg_transparent>

218
00:15:19.323 --> 00:15:22.204 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But you have to give me your word</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that no one else on this station</c.bg_transparent>

219
00:15:22.944 --> 00:15:23.665 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>will be harmed.</c.bg_transparent>

220
00:15:24.406 --> 00:15:25.943 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I... I promise.</c.bg_transparent>

221
00:15:26.862 --> 00:15:27.663 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Doctor.</c.bg_transparent>

222
00:15:30.662 --> 00:15:32.581 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Do as he says, Julian, please.</c.bg_transparent>

223
00:15:42.598 --> 00:15:44.680 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Let me treat</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Chief O'Brien's phaser wound first.</c.bg_transparent>

224
00:15:44.838 --> 00:15:45.998 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>BASHIR: It won't take long.</c.bg_transparent>

225
00:15:46.477 --> 00:15:48.517 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>There's an emergency</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>medical kit in the console.</c.bg_transparent>

226
00:15:50.797 --> 00:15:51.596 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Get it!</c.bg_transparent>

227
00:15:57.714 --> 00:15:58.634 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hold still, Chief.</c.bg_transparent>

228
00:16:01.753 --> 00:16:03.233 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( groaning )</c.bg_transparent>

229
00:16:08.391 --> 00:16:09.271 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There.</c.bg_transparent>

230
00:16:09.350 --> 00:16:11.150 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There should be no permanent damage.</c.bg_transparent>

231
00:16:14.228 --> 00:16:17.530 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Apply this every 20 minutes or so.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>It should help the wound regenerate.</c.bg_transparent>

232
00:16:17.530 --> 00:16:18.940 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Enough stalling!</c.bg_transparent>

233
00:16:19.786 --> 00:16:22.608 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Do as he says, Doctor.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>This is no time to be a hero.</c.bg_transparent>

234
00:16:23.386 --> 00:16:24.507 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Take them to the Infirmary.</c.bg_transparent>

235
00:16:26.545 --> 00:16:28.824 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This isn't over, Dax. I promise you.</c.bg_transparent>

236
00:16:29.104 --> 00:16:29.984 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>SISKO: Dax...</c.bg_transparent>

237
00:16:32.942 --> 00:16:34.022 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>DAX: I know, Benjamin.</c.bg_transparent>

238
00:16:35.062 --> 00:16:37.982 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You'll do everything you can.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>And just in case it isn't enough,</c.bg_transparent>

239
00:16:39.461 --> 00:16:40.780 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I want you to know it's been fun.</c.bg_transparent>

240
00:16:43.321 --> 00:16:44.161 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>MAREEL: Let's go.</c.bg_transparent>

241
00:16:51.118 --> 00:16:52.064 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Good luck.</c.bg_transparent>

242
00:16:52.557 --> 00:16:58.481 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It won't be long now, and then you'll see.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Everything will be just as I promised.</c.bg_transparent>

243
00:17:00.435 --> 00:17:01.394 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I know.</c.bg_transparent>

244
00:17:16.310 --> 00:17:18.269 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-What's that?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-BASHIR: It's a delta wave inducer</c.bg_transparent>

245
00:17:18.429 --> 00:17:19.950 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>to keep you asleep during the operation.</c.bg_transparent>

246
00:17:20.428 --> 00:17:22.790 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It also increases</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>your body's natural endorphin production</c.bg_transparent>

247
00:17:22.790 --> 00:17:25.371 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-to help accelerate the healing process.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I don't want it.</c.bg_transparent>

248
00:17:25.607 --> 00:17:27.168 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I strongly recommend that you use it.</c.bg_transparent>

249
00:17:27.307 --> 00:17:29.529 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The surgery</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>will be much easier on you if--</c.bg_transparent>

250
00:17:29.466 --> 00:17:31.945 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't want your advice.</c.bg_transparent>

251
00:17:33.405 --> 00:17:34.366 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I want to be awake.</c.bg_transparent>

252
00:17:35.204 --> 00:17:39.147 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Use a neuroelectrical suppresser</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and set up a monitor</c.bg_transparent>

253
00:17:39.147 --> 00:17:40.786 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>so that I can watch the procedure.</c.bg_transparent>

254
00:17:41.622 --> 00:17:43.984 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>That way, if you run into any trouble</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I can assist you.</c.bg_transparent>

255
00:17:45.501 --> 00:17:47.322 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Now, let's get started.</c.bg_transparent>

256
00:17:55.738 --> 00:17:57.057 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm sorry, Jadzia.</c.bg_transparent>

257
00:18:03.655 --> 00:18:08.174 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't blame yourself, Julian.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>You did everything you could.</c.bg_transparent>

258
00:18:08.454 --> 00:18:09.254 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I...</c.bg_transparent>

259
00:18:12.873 --> 00:18:13.914 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This will help you sleep.</c.bg_transparent>

260
00:18:13.914 --> 00:18:10.973 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Thank you.</c.bg_transparent>

261
00:18:23.791 --> 00:18:24.831 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Forgive me.</c.bg_transparent>

262
00:18:32.860 --> 00:18:34.388 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>How long can Dax survive</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>without the symbiont?</c.bg_transparent>

263
00:18:34.947 --> 00:18:38.467 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Once the symbiont is removed</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the host usually dies within hours</c.bg_transparent>

264
00:18:41.084 --> 00:18:44.567 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but Jadzia is young and healthy.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Bashir will do what he can.</c.bg_transparent>

265
00:18:46.342 --> 00:18:49.945 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-She'll make it through the night.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-That still doesn't give us much time.</c.bg_transparent>

266
00:18:50.609 --> 00:18:50.982 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No talking!</c.bg_transparent>

267
00:18:51.609 --> 00:18:51.941 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-( groaning )</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-No!</c.bg_transparent>

268
00:19:05.165 --> 00:19:06.297 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( hissing )</c.bg_transparent>

269
00:19:06.656 --> 00:19:08.155 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( loud grunting )</c.bg_transparent>

270
00:19:10.655 --> 00:19:11.895 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( groaning )</c.bg_transparent>

271
00:19:13.875 --> 00:19:15.817 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't want to kill you,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Commander, but I will!</c.bg_transparent>

272
00:20:52.165 --> 00:20:53.085 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This is ridiculous.</c.bg_transparent>

273
00:20:54.125 --> 00:20:55.804 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't you realize</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>they're going to kill us?</c.bg_transparent>

274
00:20:57.404 --> 00:20:59.203 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>What are you people sitting around for?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Do something.</c.bg_transparent>

275
00:20:59.643 --> 00:21:01.123 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Do you have any suggestions?</c.bg_transparent>

276
00:21:02.162 --> 00:21:05.508 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why should I have any suggestions?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I'm not the military mastermind.</c.bg_transparent>

277
00:21:05.841 --> 00:21:07.760 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-I'm just a victim of circumstances.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Victim? Really?</c.bg_transparent>

278
00:21:08.680 --> 00:21:11.199 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then maybe you'd like to tell me</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>how four armed terrorists</c.bg_transparent>

279
00:21:11.199 --> 00:21:13.151 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>got by our docking ring security grid.</c.bg_transparent>

280
00:21:13.159 --> 00:21:14.558 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Security grid?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I don't know anything about...</c.bg_transparent>

281
00:21:14.638 --> 00:21:17.740 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Save it, Quark.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>You crossed the line this time.</c.bg_transparent>

282
00:21:19.357 --> 00:21:22.219 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You sold us out</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and now Dax may die because of it.</c.bg_transparent>

283
00:21:22.219 --> 00:21:25.210 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, whatever happens next,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>one thing is certain you are through here.</c.bg_transparent>

284
00:21:25.297 --> 00:21:26.857 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( snarls )</c.bg_transparent>

285
00:21:37.333 --> 00:21:39.853 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Are you all right?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I'll live.</c.bg_transparent>

286
00:21:40.145 --> 00:21:42.387 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't try that again.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I don't want to have to hurt anyone.</c.bg_transparent>

287
00:21:42.610 --> 00:21:43.990 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tell that to Jadzia.</c.bg_transparent>

288
00:21:45.289 --> 00:21:46.449 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's different.</c.bg_transparent>

289
00:21:48.528 --> 00:21:49.488 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Do you really believe that?</c.bg_transparent>

290
00:21:50.228 --> 00:21:52.530 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You heard Verad.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>They didn't leave him any other choice.</c.bg_transparent>

291
00:21:52.587 --> 00:21:56.506 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-No, that's his reason. What's yours?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I owe him.</c.bg_transparent>

292
00:21:57.705 --> 00:21:59.425 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I grew up on the streets of Khefka IV.</c.bg_transparent>

293
00:21:59.505 --> 00:22:01.385 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I never would have made it out of there</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>without Verad.</c.bg_transparent>

294
00:22:01.884 --> 00:22:03.174 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What was he doing on Khefka IV?</c.bg_transparent>

295
00:22:04.544 --> 00:22:07.166 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He was the communications clerk</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>at the Federation Consulate.</c.bg_transparent>

296
00:22:07.342 --> 00:22:09.804 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He used to visit</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the accommodation house where I worked.</c.bg_transparent>

297
00:22:11.401 --> 00:22:12.522 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I used to help him relax.</c.bg_transparent>

298
00:22:14.460 --> 00:22:16.542 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>When he was recalled to Trill,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>he asked me to go with him.</c.bg_transparent>

299
00:22:17.535 --> 00:22:20.525 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-We've been together ever since.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-And that's it?</c.bg_transparent>

300
00:22:21.515 --> 00:22:25.098 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He got you out of a bad situation</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and now you're willing to kill for him?</c.bg_transparent>

301
00:22:25.697 --> 00:22:27.058 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I owe him my life.</c.bg_transparent>

302
00:22:28.416 --> 00:22:30.655 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If there's anything</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I can do for him I'll do it.</c.bg_transparent>

303
00:22:31.415 --> 00:22:33.095 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Even if it means losing him?</c.bg_transparent>

304
00:22:35.094 --> 00:22:35.974 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Losing him?</c.bg_transparent>

305
00:22:37.274 --> 00:22:40.897 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>After the surgery Verad</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>won't be just Verad anymore.</c.bg_transparent>

306
00:22:41.952 --> 00:22:45.675 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He'll be a blending of Verad, Dax,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and all the previous hosts,</c.bg_transparent>

307
00:22:46.071 --> 00:22:49.674 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>their memories, their knowledge,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>even their personalities.</c.bg_transparent>

308
00:22:50.792 --> 00:22:52.991 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Verad told me</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that you'd say things like that.</c.bg_transparent>

309
00:22:54.431 --> 00:22:55.471 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I know he'll change.</c.bg_transparent>

310
00:22:55.871 --> 00:22:58.275 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He'll be smarter, more confident,</c.bg_transparent>

311
00:22:58.110 --> 00:23:00.470 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but in all the important ways,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>he'll be the same.</c.bg_transparent>

312
00:23:00.906 --> 00:23:02.828 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm sorry,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but if he told you that, he's lying.</c.bg_transparent>

313
00:23:03.886 --> 00:23:07.269 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Once a Trill</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>is joined it's like a rebirth.</c.bg_transparent>

314
00:23:07.924 --> 00:23:09.765 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He'll be an entirely different person.</c.bg_transparent>

315
00:23:09.863 --> 00:23:12.245 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you think</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I'm going to betray Verad, you're wrong.</c.bg_transparent>

316
00:23:13.363 --> 00:23:16.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It doesn't matter</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>what you say. I love him,</c.bg_transparent>

317
00:23:17.621 --> 00:23:20.303 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and I'm going to stand</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>by him no matter what.</c.bg_transparent>

318
00:23:21.181 --> 00:23:22.381 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>VERAD: I never doubted it.</c.bg_transparent>

319
00:23:25.300 --> 00:23:26.300 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Verad.</c.bg_transparent>

320
00:23:30.258 --> 00:23:32.798 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No, not just Verad.</c.bg_transparent>

321
00:23:32.818 --> 00:23:34.298 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm Verad Dax.</c.bg_transparent>

322
00:24:02.569 --> 00:24:03.408 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Take this.</c.bg_transparent>

323
00:24:04.609 --> 00:24:07.190 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Come on, we haven't got much time.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Just move it back and forth over the wound</c.bg_transparent>

324
00:24:07.190 --> 00:24:09.160 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-in slow, even strokes.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Why bother?</c.bg_transparent>

325
00:24:09.522 --> 00:24:10.989 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>She'll be dead in a few hours anyway.</c.bg_transparent>

326
00:24:11.325 --> 00:24:13.086 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not if I have anything to do with it.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Now, help me.</c.bg_transparent>

327
00:24:13.385 --> 00:24:14.146 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why should I?</c.bg_transparent>

328
00:24:14.684 --> 00:24:17.843 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>She let herself be slaughtered</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>like a mindless </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>t'gla.</i></c.bg_transparent>

329
00:24:18.269 --> 00:24:20.731 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If she wanted to live,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>she should have fought back.</c.bg_transparent>

330
00:24:21.182 --> 00:24:23.224 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>She did what she did</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to save the rest of us.</c.bg_transparent>

331
00:24:23.442 --> 00:24:26.684 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then she is a fool,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and she deserves her fate.</c.bg_transparent>

332
00:24:26.840 --> 00:24:28.240 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Now listen to me, Yeto,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>or whatever your name is.</c.bg_transparent>

333
00:24:28.360 --> 00:24:29.400 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't give a damn</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>about your warrior ethic</c.bg_transparent>

334
00:24:29.480 --> 00:24:30.520 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>or your Klingon philosophy.</c.bg_transparent>

335
00:24:30.520 --> 00:24:32.411 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>This woman is dying,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and I need your help to save her.</c.bg_transparent>

336
00:24:32.399 --> 00:24:33.679 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Now, take this instrument.</c.bg_transparent>

337
00:24:34.679 --> 00:24:38.822 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well... so the little human</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>has some spark after all.</c.bg_transparent>

338
00:24:51.154 --> 00:24:53.313 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( beeping erratically )</c.bg_transparent>

339
00:24:54.153 --> 00:24:57.351 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Come on. Come on.</c.bg_transparent>

340
00:25:00.351 --> 00:25:02.470 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( beeping steadies )</c.bg_transparent>

341
00:25:08.748 --> 00:25:09.548 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Julian.</c.bg_transparent>

342
00:25:10.477 --> 00:25:14.580 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, thank God. I thought I'd lost you.</c.bg_transparent>

343
00:25:14.787 --> 00:25:16.266 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The symbiont.</c.bg_transparent>

344
00:25:18.985 --> 00:25:19.785 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's gone.</c.bg_transparent>

345
00:25:20.286 --> 00:25:24.749 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, everything went perfectly.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>The operation was a complete success.</c.bg_transparent>

346
00:25:26.103 --> 00:25:27.383 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I feel so alone.</c.bg_transparent>

347
00:25:28.853 --> 00:25:30.421 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've got you stabilized.</c.bg_transparent>

348
00:25:32.721 --> 00:25:34.863 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If only we could get the symbiont</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>back in time.</c.bg_transparent>

349
00:25:36.560 --> 00:25:37.760 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm scared, Julian.</c.bg_transparent>

350
00:25:39.559 --> 00:25:42.438 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're not going to die. Do you hear me?</c.bg_transparent>

351
00:25:44.758 --> 00:25:46.157 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm not going to let you die.</c.bg_transparent>

352
00:25:46.864 --> 00:25:50.715 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>( shallow breathing )</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I've never felt so empty.</c.bg_transparent>

353
00:25:54.844 --> 00:25:55.794 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>BASHIR: Just rest.</c.bg_transparent>

354
00:25:57.993 --> 00:25:58.793 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Dax?</c.bg_transparent>

355
00:26:01.073 --> 00:26:02.512 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's right, Benjamin.</c.bg_transparent>

356
00:26:04.293 --> 00:26:04.713 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's me.</c.bg_transparent>

357
00:26:07.607 --> 00:26:11.955 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Curzon, Tobin, Jadzia, all the others,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>they're all a part of you now.</c.bg_transparent>

358
00:26:12.029 --> 00:26:16.152 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's amazing.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>So many ideas. So many memories.</c.bg_transparent>

359
00:26:16.868 --> 00:26:20.351 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Eight lifetimes of memories.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>It must be incredible.</c.bg_transparent>

360
00:26:20.351 --> 00:26:22.090 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's better than I ever imagined.</c.bg_transparent>

361
00:26:22.666 --> 00:26:24.608 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The station must look very different</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to you now.</c.bg_transparent>

362
00:26:24.626 --> 00:26:28.849 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It does. I... I know this place.</c.bg_transparent>

363
00:26:31.045 --> 00:26:33.084 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( chuckling ) And I know you, Benjamin.</c.bg_transparent>

364
00:26:35.643 --> 00:26:37.603 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Of course you do.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Remember when we first met?</c.bg_transparent>

365
00:26:37.603 --> 00:26:38.888 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Pelios Station.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Anastasia?</c.bg_transparent>

366
00:26:38.888 --> 00:26:41.026 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>And that trip we took</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to the Cliffs of Bole?</c.bg_transparent>

367
00:26:41.128 --> 00:26:42.807 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( both men laughing )</c.bg_transparent>

368
00:26:43.766 --> 00:26:45.766 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>SISKO: All the months we served</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>aboard the </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Livingston.</i></c.bg_transparent>

369
00:26:45.846 --> 00:26:48.406 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>And Science Officer Kustanovich.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>What was it?</c.bg_transparent>

370
00:26:48.485 --> 00:26:50.484 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Eight helpings of Andorian Redbat?</c.bg_transparent>

371
00:26:50.644 --> 00:26:52.684 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( laughing )</c.bg_transparent>

372
00:26:53.923 --> 00:26:56.526 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>SISKO: I don't think I've ever seen</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>someone eat so much.</c.bg_transparent>

373
00:26:56.696 --> 00:26:59.498 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Remember my wedding?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I remember your bachelor party,</c.bg_transparent>

374
00:26:59.535 --> 00:27:00.734 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>or some of it anyway.</c.bg_transparent>

375
00:27:03.871 --> 00:27:05.493 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And the time we discovered the wormhole.</c.bg_transparent>

376
00:27:06.813 --> 00:27:07.653 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>My, my, my.</c.bg_transparent>

377
00:27:10.592 --> 00:27:12.233 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>One of Jadzia's proudest moments.</c.bg_transparent>

378
00:27:12.831 --> 00:27:15.353 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>And now that woman is bleeding to death</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in the Infirmary.</c.bg_transparent>

379
00:27:15.790 --> 00:27:19.653 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-I'd rather not discuss that, Benjamin.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-You have to discuss it, Dax.</c.bg_transparent>

380
00:27:20.227 --> 00:27:22.068 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You know as well as I do</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>we can't let her die.</c.bg_transparent>

381
00:27:22.237 --> 00:27:24.499 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>She's not going to die.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>She'll live on in me.</c.bg_transparent>

382
00:27:25.580 --> 00:27:26.990 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Jadzia's memories will live on,</c.bg_transparent>

383
00:27:27.706 --> 00:27:31.009 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but Jadzia herself will die,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and you'll have killed her.</c.bg_transparent>

384
00:27:31.486 --> 00:27:34.508 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You think I don't know that?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I'll never be able to forget it,</c.bg_transparent>

385
00:27:36.144 --> 00:27:39.066 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but I promise you, Benjamin</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I'll do all I can to make up for it.</c.bg_transparent>

386
00:27:39.103 --> 00:27:41.205 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm not going</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to the Gamma Quadrant to hide.</c.bg_transparent>

387
00:27:41.842 --> 00:27:46.245 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>There are entire worlds who can benefit</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>from my knowledge and experience.</c.bg_transparent>

388
00:27:46.345 --> 00:27:49.980 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-I can help them, and I will.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I have a better idea.</c.bg_transparent>

389
00:27:50.000 --> 00:27:52.599 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-VERAD: What's that?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Help Jadzia.</c.bg_transparent>

390
00:27:53.659 --> 00:27:57.462 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Come with me down to the Infirmary.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Put the symbiont back where it belongs.</c.bg_transparent>

391
00:27:59.038 --> 00:28:01.640 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I can't do that, Benjamin,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>even if I wanted to.</c.bg_transparent>

392
00:28:01.640 --> 00:28:05.050 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't you see? It's too late.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>The integration is already underway.</c.bg_transparent>

393
00:28:05.375 --> 00:28:09.098 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But there's still time to stop it.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Jadzia's life can still be saved.</c.bg_transparent>

394
00:28:09.098 --> 00:28:11.558 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't listen to him.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>He's just trying to confuse you.</c.bg_transparent>

395
00:28:11.617 --> 00:28:12.890 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's all right, Mareel.</c.bg_transparent>

396
00:28:13.434 --> 00:28:16.456 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Benjamin, the symbiont is still weak</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>from the operation.</c.bg_transparent>

397
00:28:16.456 --> 00:28:20.760 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If we attempt another joining so soon,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>it might not survive.</c.bg_transparent>

398
00:28:21.522 --> 00:28:23.627 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-VERAD: Are you willing to risk that?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I am.</c.bg_transparent>

399
00:28:25.226 --> 00:28:27.665 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The question is, are you?</c.bg_transparent>

400
00:28:28.265 --> 00:28:30.385 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why are you wasting your time with him?</c.bg_transparent>

401
00:28:30.465 --> 00:28:31.944 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Because he's my friend!</c.bg_transparent>

402
00:28:32.384 --> 00:28:33.944 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Now, go watch the others.</c.bg_transparent>

403
00:28:39.606 --> 00:28:41.375 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We are still friends, aren't we, Benjamin?</c.bg_transparent>

404
00:28:42.498 --> 00:28:43.139 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I hope so.</c.bg_transparent>

405
00:28:44.864 --> 00:28:46.525 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Come with me down to the Infirmary</c.bg_transparent>

406
00:28:46.603 --> 00:28:47.364 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>and prove it.</c.bg_transparent>

407
00:28:50.243 --> 00:28:51.043 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I can't do that.</c.bg_transparent>

408
00:28:55.400 --> 00:29:01.304 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then you're not the Dax that I know.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Our friendship is over.</c.bg_transparent>

409
00:29:29.459 --> 00:29:31.852 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Here, drink this.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-What is it?</c.bg_transparent>

410
00:29:32.958 --> 00:29:34.974 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Senarian egg broth.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>It'll keep your strength up.</c.bg_transparent>

411
00:29:36.614 --> 00:29:38.973 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>All right, don't drink it.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>It makes no difference to me.</c.bg_transparent>

412
00:29:39.253 --> 00:29:40.053 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hold on.</c.bg_transparent>

413
00:29:41.213 --> 00:29:42.213 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Thank you.</c.bg_transparent>

414
00:29:52.490 --> 00:29:54.249 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He even looks different, doesn't he?</c.bg_transparent>

415
00:29:55.408 --> 00:29:58.928 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The way he stands,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the way he moves, talks.</c.bg_transparent>

416
00:29:59.087 --> 00:30:02.446 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-He's better than he was.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I'm glad you think so.</c.bg_transparent>

417
00:30:04.258 --> 00:30:04.165 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I do.</c.bg_transparent>

418
00:30:04.799 --> 00:30:07.521 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Really? The way he dismissed you before?</c.bg_transparent>

419
00:30:07.962 --> 00:30:10.921 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Verad never did that.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-He's under a lot of stress.</c.bg_transparent>

420
00:30:11.501 --> 00:30:13.840 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>SISKO:</c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i> </i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>Verad was under stress</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the minute he stepped onto this station,</c.bg_transparent>

421
00:30:14.837 --> 00:30:17.279 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-but he never turned on you, did he?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-What's your point, Commander?</c.bg_transparent>

422
00:30:17.296 --> 00:30:17.957 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I think you know.</c.bg_transparent>

423
00:30:17.957 --> 00:30:19.596 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're trying to turn me against Verad.</c.bg_transparent>

424
00:30:21.578 --> 00:30:23.977 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Verad no longer exists.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>You know that better than I do.</c.bg_transparent>

425
00:30:24.154 --> 00:30:26.496 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>All right, then.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Verad Dax, but it won't work.</c.bg_transparent>

426
00:30:27.392 --> 00:30:30.432 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Nothing has changed between us.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-You really believe that?</c.bg_transparent>

427
00:30:30.872 --> 00:30:31.671 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes.</c.bg_transparent>

428
00:30:33.990 --> 00:30:35.031 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>All right.</c.bg_transparent>

429
00:30:36.590 --> 00:30:37.751 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then make me believe it.</c.bg_transparent>

430
00:30:39.330 --> 00:30:40.851 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Go in there and talk to him.</c.bg_transparent>

431
00:30:43.089 --> 00:30:44.529 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Talk to him about what?</c.bg_transparent>

432
00:30:45.317 --> 00:30:46.409 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't know. Whatever you want.</c.bg_transparent>

433
00:30:46.409 --> 00:30:48.610 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm sure the two of you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>have a lot to say to one another.</c.bg_transparent>

434
00:30:52.322 --> 00:30:54.023 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-I don't want to disturb him.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Why not?</c.bg_transparent>

435
00:30:54.365 --> 00:30:55.764 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Because I don't want to!</c.bg_transparent>

436
00:30:56.966 --> 00:30:59.046 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, look at him,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>sitting in there all alone.</c.bg_transparent>

437
00:30:59.326 --> 00:31:01.164 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-He needs you.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-That's enough.</c.bg_transparent>

438
00:31:01.424 --> 00:31:03.465 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't understand</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>why you're being so reluctant.</c.bg_transparent>

439
00:31:03.703 --> 00:31:05.943 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>This is the perfect time</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for the two of you to get reacquainted.</c.bg_transparent>

440
00:31:05.943 --> 00:31:07.701 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-I said that's enough!</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-VERAD: Mareel.</c.bg_transparent>

441
00:31:10.816 --> 00:31:11.422 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is anything wrong?</c.bg_transparent>

442
00:31:11.702 --> 00:31:13.341 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No, everything's fine.</c.bg_transparent>

443
00:31:14.301 --> 00:31:15.100 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Good.</c.bg_transparent>

444
00:31:17.078 --> 00:31:17.698 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Be careful.</c.bg_transparent>

445
00:31:18.619 --> 00:31:20.260 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I wouldn't want anything to happen to you.</c.bg_transparent>

446
00:31:37.213 --> 00:31:38.773 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( grunting and groaning )</c.bg_transparent>

447
00:31:39.772 --> 00:31:41.652 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I got him! I got him!</c.bg_transparent>

448
00:31:42.571 --> 00:31:43.811 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( roaring )</c.bg_transparent>

449
00:31:44.713 --> 00:31:45.331 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Stay back.</c.bg_transparent>

450
00:31:45.850 --> 00:31:48.105 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( groaning )</c.bg_transparent>

451
00:31:49.089 --> 00:31:51.008 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Maybe we should talk about this, huh?</c.bg_transparent>

452
00:31:51.808 --> 00:31:52.848 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( grunts )</c.bg_transparent>

453
00:31:55.727 --> 00:31:56.807 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>My ear.</c.bg_transparent>

454
00:31:57.527 --> 00:31:59.126 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( moaning )</c.bg_transparent>

455
00:32:02.405 --> 00:32:03.285 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Pathetic.</c.bg_transparent>

456
00:32:04.245 --> 00:32:06.804 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mareel, take him to the Infirmary.</c.bg_transparent>

457
00:32:07.244 --> 00:32:08.764 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( moaning )</c.bg_transparent>

458
00:32:18.461 --> 00:32:19.401 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-( screaming )</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-What is it now?</c.bg_transparent>

459
00:32:21.579 --> 00:32:23.459 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Please... it hurts.</c.bg_transparent>

460
00:32:24.219 --> 00:32:25.899 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>All right. Hold on.</c.bg_transparent>

461
00:32:29.137 --> 00:32:31.016 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The damage</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>appears to be fairly superficial.</c.bg_transparent>

462
00:32:32.177 --> 00:32:33.296 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( whispering ) No.</c.bg_transparent>

463
00:32:34.176 --> 00:32:39.495 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But Ferengi ears are incredibly sensitive.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>So I'd better run some further tests.</c.bg_transparent>

464
00:32:39.615 --> 00:32:41.201 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( moaning loudly )</c.bg_transparent>

465
00:32:46.431 --> 00:32:48.441 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The storm's intensity's dropped</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>another 20%.</c.bg_transparent>

466
00:32:51.331 --> 00:32:53.032 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I know this has been</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>hard for you, Benjamin.</c.bg_transparent>

467
00:32:53.110 --> 00:32:55.751 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's been hard for both of us</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but it's almost over.</c.bg_transparent>

468
00:32:56.069 --> 00:32:56.869 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>MAREEL: Good.</c.bg_transparent>

469
00:32:57.509 --> 00:32:59.010 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm getting tired of waiting here.</c.bg_transparent>

470
00:33:02.028 --> 00:33:05.386 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-How are you feeling?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Better than ever, thanks to you.</c.bg_transparent>

471
00:33:06.586 --> 00:33:07.866 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I couldn't have done this without you.</c.bg_transparent>

472
00:33:08.726 --> 00:33:11.908 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I would have spent the rest</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of my life a mediocre man</c.bg_transparent>

473
00:33:11.908 --> 00:33:13.687 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>only dreaming about what might have been.</c.bg_transparent>

474
00:33:16.104 --> 00:33:17.044 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You know what you have to do.</c.bg_transparent>

475
00:33:18.391 --> 00:33:19.342 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You just worry about getting</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>through the wormhole.</c.bg_transparent>

476
00:33:20.298 --> 00:33:21.730 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Klingons and I will make sure</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that no one stops you.</c.bg_transparent>

477
00:33:21.821 --> 00:33:25.303 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Remember, I don't want you staying here</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>any longer than you have to.</c.bg_transparent>

478
00:33:25.380 --> 00:33:27.501 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Give me an hour,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>then head for the wormhole.</c.bg_transparent>

479
00:33:27.580 --> 00:33:28.860 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The runabout's on Pad C.</c.bg_transparent>

480
00:33:28.939 --> 00:33:31.059 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The sooner you leave,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the sooner I can follow</c.bg_transparent>

481
00:33:31.619 --> 00:33:32.938 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>and the sooner we'll be together.</c.bg_transparent>

482
00:33:39.115 --> 00:33:40.375 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's going to be all right, isn't it?</c.bg_transparent>

483
00:33:42.694 --> 00:33:44.496 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Just wait for me at the rendezvous point.</c.bg_transparent>

484
00:34:01.609 --> 00:34:02.569 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( loud moaning )</c.bg_transparent>

485
00:34:02.989 --> 00:34:05.631 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Stop whining</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>or I'll put you out of your misery.</c.bg_transparent>

486
00:34:05.688 --> 00:34:06.708 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's not his fault.</c.bg_transparent>

487
00:34:06.708 --> 00:34:08.007 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He's got a deep contusion</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of the auricular lobe</c.bg_transparent>

488
00:34:08.147 --> 00:34:09.627 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>and a possible dislocated malleus.</c.bg_transparent>

489
00:34:09.926 --> 00:34:12.228 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>In a Ferengi, either condition</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>could be fatal.</c.bg_transparent>

490
00:34:13.785 --> 00:34:16.387 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But if you want him to stop,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>give me a hand with this.</c.bg_transparent>

491
00:34:16.504 --> 00:34:18.143 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm not your nurse!</c.bg_transparent>

492
00:34:18.203 --> 00:34:21.866 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Look, let's not go through that again.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Just hold this against his ear.</c.bg_transparent>

493
00:34:21.843 --> 00:34:23.762 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( high-pitched whining )</c.bg_transparent>

494
00:34:26.201 --> 00:34:27.400 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( screams )</c.bg_transparent>

495
00:34:27.822 --> 00:34:29.162 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not too hard.</c.bg_transparent>

496
00:34:31.580 --> 00:34:32.792 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( groaning )</c.bg_transparent>

497
00:34:33.588 --> 00:34:34.020 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Just another second.</c.bg_transparent>

498
00:34:37.119 --> 00:34:37.659 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Relax.</c.bg_transparent>

499
00:34:39.318 --> 00:34:40.518 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( gasps )</c.bg_transparent>

500
00:34:44.577 --> 00:34:44.517 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There.</c.bg_transparent>

501
00:34:46.217 --> 00:34:49.339 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Thank you, Doctor. I feel better already.</c.bg_transparent>

502
00:34:53.927 --> 00:34:54.135 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How is she?</c.bg_transparent>

503
00:34:55.773 --> 00:34:56.673 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I have her stabilized</c.bg_transparent>

504
00:34:56.673 --> 00:34:58.444 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but there's no telling</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>how much time she has left.</c.bg_transparent>

505
00:35:00.326 --> 00:35:01.952 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We've got to get the symbiont</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>back before it's too late.</c.bg_transparent>

506
00:35:02.591 --> 00:35:04.590 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-What are you doing?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Odo's in here.</c.bg_transparent>

507
00:35:05.150 --> 00:35:05.950 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He is?</c.bg_transparent>

508
00:35:05.950 --> 00:35:07.691 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes, and we've got to get him out.</c.bg_transparent>

509
00:35:08.909 --> 00:35:10.668 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Are you sure?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Quark!</c.bg_transparent>

510
00:35:13.214 --> 00:35:13.668 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>If only we knew the access code.</c.bg_transparent>

511
00:35:16.548 --> 00:35:18.194 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Allow me.</c.bg_transparent>

512
00:35:23.105 --> 00:35:25.771 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( beeping softly )</c.bg_transparent>

513
00:35:31.325 --> 00:35:35.007 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ah... standard</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Delgorian locking mechanism.</c.bg_transparent>

514
00:35:35.202 --> 00:35:36.422 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sophisticated...</c.bg_transparent>

515
00:35:37.921 --> 00:35:39.682 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>but vulnerable if you know its weaknesses.</c.bg_transparent>

516
00:35:40.200 --> 00:35:41.680 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hand me that laser scalpel.</c.bg_transparent>

517
00:35:46.798 --> 00:35:47.718 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Uh-huh.</c.bg_transparent>

518
00:35:51.996 --> 00:35:52.797 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mm-hmm.</c.bg_transparent>

519
00:35:53.316 --> 00:35:54.755 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( clicking )</c.bg_transparent>

520
00:35:54.836 --> 00:35:56.275 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( beeping )</c.bg_transparent>

521
00:35:56.915 --> 00:35:57.955 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( lock releases )</c.bg_transparent>

522
00:36:00.674 --> 00:36:01.674 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's a gift.</c.bg_transparent>

523
00:36:01.691 --> 00:36:03.730 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The storm's decreased another 15%.</c.bg_transparent>

524
00:36:05.451 --> 00:36:09.134 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Excellent. That should be more than enough</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to allow safe passage to the wormhole.</c.bg_transparent>

525
00:36:09.930 --> 00:36:10.770 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Verad to Yeto.</c.bg_transparent>

526
00:36:13.049 --> 00:36:14.648 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Verad to Yeto.</c.bg_transparent>

527
00:36:15.951 --> 00:36:16.850 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yeto, report!</c.bg_transparent>

528
00:36:16.850 --> 00:36:19.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The doctor must have overpowered him.</c.bg_transparent>

529
00:36:19.327 --> 00:36:21.929 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-The doctor? Impossible.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-It's the shape-shifter.</c.bg_transparent>

530
00:36:21.929 --> 00:36:24.780 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He must have freed the shape-shifter.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>T'Kar, get me to the ship.</c.bg_transparent>

531
00:36:26.006 --> 00:36:28.388 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You'd better take a hostage just in case.</c.bg_transparent>

532
00:36:28.543 --> 00:36:29.425 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll go with you.</c.bg_transparent>

533
00:36:29.445 --> 00:36:31.243 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>VERAD: I'd love your company, Benjamin,</c.bg_transparent>

534
00:36:31.242 --> 00:36:33.688 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but somehow, I don't think you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>have my best interests at heart.</c.bg_transparent>

535
00:36:33.708 --> 00:36:36.268 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Kira, I hate to inconvenience you--</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-That's all right.</c.bg_transparent>

536
00:36:37.483 --> 00:36:39.824 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If Odo's free there's no way</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you're getting off this station.</c.bg_transparent>

537
00:36:44.921 --> 00:36:45.720 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mareel?</c.bg_transparent>

538
00:36:47.000 --> 00:36:48.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Good luck.</c.bg_transparent>

539
00:36:50.359 --> 00:36:52.160 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, Benjamin, I guess this is good-bye.</c.bg_transparent>

540
00:36:52.898 --> 00:36:55.239 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not many friendships</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>last over two lifetimes.</c.bg_transparent>

541
00:36:57.157 --> 00:36:58.476 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I wish we could have made it three.</c.bg_transparent>

542
00:36:59.316 --> 00:37:01.196 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You'll be seeing me again, Verad.</c.bg_transparent>

543
00:37:24.469 --> 00:37:25.469 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>So...</c.bg_transparent>

544
00:37:26.868 --> 00:37:28.708 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Where's this rendezvous going to be?</c.bg_transparent>

545
00:37:30.126 --> 00:37:34.149 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-You don't really expect me to tell you.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-No, but I hope you like it there,</c.bg_transparent>

546
00:37:34.626 --> 00:37:37.407 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>because you'll be waiting</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for Verad a long time.</c.bg_transparent>

547
00:37:37.789 --> 00:37:40.611 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-How would you know?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-You told me yourself.</c.bg_transparent>

548
00:37:42.244 --> 00:37:44.585 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I saw the look on your face</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>when he asked you to wait for him.</c.bg_transparent>

549
00:37:48.042 --> 00:37:50.081 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The plan was, he was supposed</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to get there first.</c.bg_transparent>

550
00:37:52.068 --> 00:37:53.554 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>That he would wait for me,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>not the other way around.</c.bg_transparent>

551
00:37:53.994 --> 00:37:58.913 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, maybe it was an honest mistake.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>A slip of the tongue.</c.bg_transparent>

552
00:37:59.112 --> 00:38:01.472 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No. He lied to me.</c.bg_transparent>

553
00:38:04.030 --> 00:38:05.590 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He's never lied to me before.</c.bg_transparent>

554
00:38:07.550 --> 00:38:08.549 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He's not coming.</c.bg_transparent>

555
00:38:10.709 --> 00:38:12.069 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He doesn't need me anymore.</c.bg_transparent>

556
00:38:12.828 --> 00:38:14.788 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No, you're wrong.</c.bg_transparent>

557
00:38:16.473 --> 00:38:18.654 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He does need you now, more than ever.</c.bg_transparent>

558
00:38:21.471 --> 00:38:22.612 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You never give up, do you?</c.bg_transparent>

559
00:38:24.491 --> 00:38:27.933 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-I told you, I'm not going to betray him.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I'm not asking you to.</c.bg_transparent>

560
00:38:28.510 --> 00:38:31.411 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm asking you to save him,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to help us save him.</c.bg_transparent>

561
00:38:31.411 --> 00:38:32.689 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>All you care about is Jadzia.</c.bg_transparent>

562
00:38:33.287 --> 00:38:36.690 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's right, and you care about Verad,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and we can save them both.</c.bg_transparent>

563
00:38:38.367 --> 00:38:39.167 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't you see?</c.bg_transparent>

564
00:38:40.826 --> 00:38:42.947 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Dax and Verad</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>were never meant to be joined.</c.bg_transparent>

565
00:38:43.408 --> 00:38:46.310 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We've got to remove the symbiont</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>while there's still time.</c.bg_transparent>

566
00:38:50.806 --> 00:38:51.886 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you hurt him...</c.bg_transparent>

567
00:38:54.605 --> 00:38:55.405 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll kill you.</c.bg_transparent>

568
00:39:01.720 --> 00:39:02.540 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't doubt it.</c.bg_transparent>

569
00:39:26.313 --> 00:39:28.312 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The ship... it's gone.</c.bg_transparent>

570
00:39:28.392 --> 00:39:30.471 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's because I released</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the docking clamps.</c.bg_transparent>

571
00:39:48.624 --> 00:39:50.686 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Looks like that good-bye</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>was a little premature.</c.bg_transparent>

572
00:39:51.305 --> 00:39:53.546 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't be ridiculous.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>You're not going to shoot me.</c.bg_transparent>

573
00:39:54.395 --> 00:39:55.684 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What makes you so sure?</c.bg_transparent>

574
00:39:56.323 --> 00:39:58.664 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This is Dax you're talking to, Benjamin.</c.bg_transparent>

575
00:39:59.342 --> 00:40:01.843 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We both know that if you shoot me,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>even on stun,</c.bg_transparent>

576
00:40:02.561 --> 00:40:04.302 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>you risk killing the symbiont.</c.bg_transparent>

577
00:40:05.320 --> 00:40:08.202 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>If I let you go, Jadzia dies.</c.bg_transparent>

578
00:40:08.960 --> 00:40:10.021 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But Dax will live.</c.bg_transparent>

579
00:40:11.159 --> 00:40:13.680 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>What's one girl's life</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>compared to eight lifetimes</c.bg_transparent>

580
00:40:13.838 --> 00:40:15.339 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>of knowledge and experience?</c.bg_transparent>

581
00:40:18.517 --> 00:40:22.076 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're not going to shoot me.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>You know that, and so do I.</c.bg_transparent>

582
00:40:25.994 --> 00:40:27.434 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Good-bye, Benjamin.</c.bg_transparent>

583
00:40:30.913 --> 00:40:31.753 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Verad.</c.bg_transparent>

584
00:40:38.430 --> 00:40:40.851 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't call me Benjamin.</c.bg_transparent>

585
00:40:40.950 --> 00:40:42.350 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( groans )</c.bg_transparent>

586
00:41:02.603 --> 00:41:03.603 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I feel strange.</c.bg_transparent>

587
00:41:05.742 --> 00:41:06.362 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>So empty.</c.bg_transparent>

588
00:41:07.122 --> 00:41:10.764 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's over now, Verad.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>The symbiont is back where it belongs.</c.bg_transparent>

589
00:41:12.880 --> 00:41:13.641 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>So close.</c.bg_transparent>

590
00:41:16.319 --> 00:41:17.557 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I had it.</c.bg_transparent>

591
00:41:19.517 --> 00:41:20.917 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I had it, and...</c.bg_transparent>

592
00:41:24.332 --> 00:41:25.275 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Now I'm alone.</c.bg_transparent>

593
00:41:26.527 --> 00:41:27.755 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're not alone, Verad.</c.bg_transparent>

594
00:41:29.355 --> 00:41:30.274 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm here.</c.bg_transparent>

595
00:41:32.195 --> 00:41:33.235 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll always be here.</c.bg_transparent>

596
00:41:36.214 --> 00:41:37.743 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I can't remember any of it.</c.bg_transparent>

597
00:41:42.052 --> 00:41:42.851 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The knowledge...</c.bg_transparent>

598
00:41:45.290 --> 00:41:46.290 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The confidence...</c.bg_transparent>

599
00:41:49.399 --> 00:41:50.665 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's all gone.</c.bg_transparent>

600
00:41:51.649 --> 00:41:52.449 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>BASHIR: Commander?</c.bg_transparent>

601
00:41:59.406 --> 00:42:00.246 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Jadzia.</c.bg_transparent>

602
00:42:05.605 --> 00:42:06.524 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Are you?</c.bg_transparent>

603
00:42:07.247 --> 00:42:07.844 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm fine.</c.bg_transparent>

604
00:42:10.503 --> 00:42:15.406 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I remember it all, Benjamin,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>everything he thought, everything he did,</c.bg_transparent>

605
00:42:16.901 --> 00:42:18.181 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>and it's so sad.</c.bg_transparent>

606
00:42:23.339 --> 00:42:24.836 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I guess...</c.bg_transparent>

607
00:42:26.398 --> 00:42:27.538 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He'll always be with me.</c.bg_transparent>

